data.description: Take me home, country roads…Situated on right under 5.5 acres, highlighting both prairie and mountain views, this country oasis provides a quiet and peaceful setting. The front porch has been decorated with a surrounding quaint rock garden and classic cement steps. Upon entry, laminate flooring has been installed throughout the entire home for an easy maintenance up-keep. The home has been freshly painted on the interior, including all doors. The great room presents vaulted ceilings, accenting its spacious interior. A contemporary new electric fireplace has been installed, with its design coordinating and complimenting the newly renovated kitchen. New cabinets, countertops, dishwasher, oven hood, and custom built and designed island have modernized the home to its fullest potential. An accented wood wall has been designed to bring together and finalize the kitchen vision. The guest bathroom has been updated with tile flooring and charming textured walls. The oversized, separate laundry room has plenty of space for washing, folding, organizing, and attending to your everyday laundry commitments. A brand new heating and cooling system has been installed for year round convenience. With a rare and very advantageous 4-car detached garage and oversized storage shed, this property officially has everything you need. In addition to RV parking and space for all the motorized toys you can think of, the garage also offers a 220v plug, shop air hook-ups, wall heater, and concrete flooring. The additional shed provides a large loft that can be utilized for extra storage, tools, or however the space fits your needs. Zoned for horses, this incredible property provides endless opportunities to enjoy all that county living has to offer.
